---
import Icon from "./Icon.astro";
---

<section class="box skills">
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon
			icon="terminal-window"
			color="var(--accent-regular)"
			size="2.5rem"
			gradient
		/>
		<h2>Infrastructure & Operations</h2>
		<p>
			Ensuring trading systems run at peak performance. Monitoring, debugging,
			and optimizing high-frequency infrastructure with Kubernetes, Prometheus,
			Grafana, and Kafka.
		</p>
	</div>
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon
			icon="code"
			color="var(--accent-regular)"
			size="2.5rem"
			gradient
		/>
		<h2>Systems Programming</h2>
		<p>
			Building low-latency tools and automation in Rust and Python.
			From rapid debugging scripts to production-grade system utilities
			and trading infrastructure.
		</p>
	</div>
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon
			icon="strategy"
			color="var(--accent-regular)"
			size="2.5rem"
			gradient
		/>
		<h2>Result-driven</h2>
		<p>
			Thriving under pressure in fast-paced trading environments.
			Composed during market opens, disciplined in execution,
			always learning and improving.
		</p>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.box {
		border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
		border-radius: var(--radius-md);
		padding: 1.5rem;
		background: var(--glass-bg);
		backdrop-filter: blur(var(--glass-blur));
		-webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(var(--glass-blur));
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
	}

	.skills {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 3rem;
	}

	.skills h2 {
		font-size: var(--text-lg);
	}

	.skills p {
		color: var(--gray-400);
		line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
	}

	/* Hover effect for skill sections */
	.skills > div {
		padding: 1rem;
		border-radius: var(--radius-md);
		transition: all var(--transition-normal);
	}

	.skills > div:hover {
		background: var(--accent-subtle-overlay);
		transform: translateY(-2px);
	}

	@media (min-width: 50em) {
		.box {
			border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
			padding: 2.5rem;
		}

		.skills {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
			gap: 5rem;
		}

		.skills h2 {
			font-size: var(--text-2xl);
		}
	}
</style>
